  • Constructor Details

    • HrfDLReader

      public HrfDLReader​(Path file, DLCore core) throws IOException, DLException
      This reader is reading the DL Human Readable Format.ATTENTION: The file is loaded as String before parsing. Be aware to have enough RAM for large files.
      Parameters:
      file - file to read the content from
      core - core as context
      Throws:
      IOException - if file can not be read
      DLException - if the content can not be parsed
